sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant B as Browser
    participant N as Next.js (RSC)
    participant M as Middleware
    participant A as NextAuth /api/auth
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>B: Buka /login
    B->>N: GET /login
    N-->>B: Render LoginForm
    U->>B: Isi email + password, submit
    B->>A: POST /api/auth/callback/credentials
    A->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE email=?
    DB-->>A: row(user)
    A->>A: bcrypt.compare(password, user.password)
    alt password valid
        A->>A: Sign JWT { sub, role, email }
        A-->>B: Set-Cookie: next-auth.session-token
        B->>N: GET /
        N->>M: middleware(req)
        M->>M: cek session + role
        M-->>N: NextResponse.next()
        N-->>B: Render Dashboard
    else password invalid
        A-->>B: 401 Unauthorized
        B-->>U: Tampilkan toast error
    end
